<chapter xml:id="ch-linear-inequalities" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>Linear Inequalities</title>

  <introduction>
    <p>
      In Grade 9, you learned how to compare quantities that are not strictly equal. In this section, we will review simple linear inequalities in one unknown and the rules for solving them.
    </p>
  </introduction>

